 @{" " link "'#toc0'/MAIN"}Name listbasic - Extract the BASIC from a ZX Spectrum file @{" " link "'#toc1'/MAIN"}Synopsis @{"b"}listbasic@{"ub"} @{"i"}file@{"ui"} 

@{" " link "'#toc2'/MAIN"}Description Listbasic extracts the BASIC listing from a ZX Spectrum snapshot or tape file and prints it to standard output. @{" " link "'#toc3'/MAIN"}Options @{"i"}file@{"ui"} specifies a snapshot or tape image from which to extract the BASIC, which must be in a format supported by @{" " link "'libspectrum.3'/MAIN"}@{"i"}libspectrum@{"ui"}(3) . @{" " link "'#toc4'/MAIN"}Bugs None known. @{" " link "'#toc5'/MAIN"}See Also @{" " link "'fuse.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}fuse@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'fuse-utils.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}fuse-utils@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'libspectrum.3'/MAIN"}@{"i"}libspectrum@{"ui"}(3) 

The comp.sys.sinclair Spectrum FAQ, at 
@{" " link "'http://www.worldofspectrum.org/faq/index.html.guide/MAIN"}@{"i"}http://www.worldofspectrum.org/faq/index.html@{"ui"}. @{" " link "'#toc6'/MAIN"}Author Philip Kendall (philip-fuse@shadowmagic.org.uk). 

Chris Cowley wrote @{"i"}SnapList@{"ui"}, (@{"i"}http://freestuff.grok.co.uk/snaplist/index.html@{"ui"}), @{"i"}@{"ui"}on which listbasic is very heavily based. 


